Sun Jul 14 12:59:27 1996  Roland McGrath  <roland@delasyd.gnu.ai.mit.edu>

	* job.c (construct_command_argv_internal): Fix up #else, #endifs.

	* configh.dos: Define HAVE_DIRENT_H instead of DIRENT.

