	--warn-undefined-variables around expansion of SHELL and IFS.
	* read.c (tilde_expand): Likewise for HOME.
	(read_all_makefiles): Likewise for MAKEFILES.
	* vpath.c (build_vpath_lists): Likewise for VPATH.

